<br>
Haste: Bronze<br>
<br>
20% haste.  Affects bronze and rusty weapons.  This effect can be found on haste items dropped by level 20-40 mobs.<br>
<br>
Haste: Fine Steel<br>
<br>
20% haste.  Affects fine steel, bronze and rusty weapons.  This effect can be found on haste items dropped by level 35-55 mobs.<br>
<br>
Haste: Ultimate<br>
<br>
20% haste.  Affects all weapons.  This effect can be found on items dropped by mobs that can only be assaulted by a full level sixty raiding force.<br>
<br>
This analogy pretty accurately reflects what druids get with Improved Healing.  The obtainability gap between focuses that work for Greater Healing and the higher focus items that work our post-30 heals is huge, even though the heals are pretty mediocre to begin with in the grand scheme of things.<br>
<br>
